thread.title_full: Totally Wicked E-liquid USA inc. reviewed by Jay

author: Jay
title: Jay
text: I like the variety offered by Totally Wicked and the prices are much lower than shops in my area. Shipping is usually pretty quick but once in a while it takes ages for my things to arrive. This isn't a big deal but it is worth noting. Overall, a great company to do business with.
